---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="AI Disclaimer - Teacher Jake" 
  currentLang="english" 
  currentTag="all"
  description="Understanding how Teacher Jake uses AI to enhance educational materials."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 mt-8 mb-12 px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#06422f] mb-8 tracking-tight">AI Generated Content Disclaimer</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-emerald max-w-none text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-serif">
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">At Teacher Jake, we leverage artificial intelligence to help create engaging, diverse, and interactive learning materials for students and teachers worldwide.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-10 mb-4 font-sans">How We Use AI</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We use AI-assisted tools to help with:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Generating high-quality, illustrative images for worksheets and activities.</li>
        <li>Drafting reading passages and exercises adapted to different proficiency levels.</li>
        <li>Creating interactive scenarios and quizzes to enhance student engagement.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-10 mb-4 font-sans">Accuracy and Curation</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">While AI allows us to provide a vast range of content, we understand its limitations. We strive to curate and review AI-generated materials for educational accuracy and appropriateness. However, we always recommend that teachers and students review materials before use in a classroom setting.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-10 mb-4 font-sans">Our Commitment</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">Our goal is to use these modern tools to make language learning more accessible, fun, and effective. We are committed to transparency in how our resources are developed.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
